<b>Watton-at-Stone railway station</b> serves the village of <site wordnetid="108651247" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../016/2330016.xml">
Watton-at-Stone</link></site>
 in <county wordnetid="108546183" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
